         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832"><!-- p3l1-r5 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De meditatione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
      ¶ De meditatione. Rubrica i.<!-- dbcheck; this seems like 5 -->
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="4"/><ref>SAlomon in eccl. c. 12. et
      <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>fine.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e127">Frequens
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>meditatio carnis est afflictio.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>
             ¶ <ref>Aristoteles de memoria et remis.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e137">Meditationes memoriam saluant in remini
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>scendo: hoc autem nil est alterum quam speculari.
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>multotiens sicut imaginem: et non sicut per se</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
             ¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 30.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e152">Ante tem
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>pus senectam adducit cogitatus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
             ¶ <ref>Mattheus in euangel. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e162">Ubi est thesau
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>rus tuus: ibi et cor tuum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
             ¶ <ref>Seneca de ira li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e172">Nihil est difficile et ar
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>duum quod non humana mens vincat: et in fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>miliaritatem perducat assidua cogitatio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>
             ¶ <ref>Uegecius de re militari lib. i. ti. 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e184">Nihil
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>est quod non assidua medicatio facillimum red
        <lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>dat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e192"> /
               <ref>Libro. 2 ti. 23. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e194">Antiqua est pru
        <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>densque sententia <sic>omnea</sic> artes in meditatio
        <lb ed="#V" n="22" break="no"/>ne consistere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e202">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
             ¶ <ref>Prouerb. vulg.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e206">Chi a porcel perdu: spesse
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>fiae ge roze al cul.</quote>
            </p>
    
